00:27:07.594 --> 00:27:09.010
GARY CATONA: The
problem is what's

00:27:09.010 --> 00:27:11.800
happening is your larynx
is rising over time,

00:27:11.800 --> 00:27:13.170
which makes your voice rise.

00:27:13.170 --> 00:27:16.062
So the way you deal with that
is doing certain exercises which

00:27:16.062 --> 00:27:16.770
drop your larynx.

00:27:16.770 --> 00:27:18.150
