00:27:18.150 --> 00:27:20.060
Put your finger on
your Adam's apple.

00:27:20.060 --> 00:27:21.660
Everybody do it.

00:27:21.660 --> 00:27:22.670
Everybody go ooh.

00:27:22.670 --> 00:27:22.920
AUDIENCE: Ooh.

00:27:22.920 --> 00:27:24.320
GARY CATONA: Where does
the Adam's apple go?

00:27:24.320 --> 00:27:24.990
AUDIENCE: Down.

00:27:24.990 --> 00:27:25.740
GARY CATONA: Down.

00:27:25.740 --> 00:27:26.980
So watch this exercise.

00:27:26.980 --> 00:27:27.972
[SINGING] Oooooooh.

00:27:35.412 --> 00:27:35.977
See it?

00:27:35.977 --> 00:27:37.560
AUDIENCE: And run
