00:27:37.560 --> 00:27:38.040
GARY CATONA: Run
through that cycle.

00:27:38.040 --> 00:27:41.140
Do it like three or four notes,
up and back, very, very slowly,

00:27:41.140 --> 00:27:41.937
full voice.

00:27:41.937 --> 00:27:43.270
And it'll help you a great deal.

