Ready?

00:37:12.070 --> 00:37:13.024
Go, uh.

00:37:13.024 --> 00:37:13.565
AUDIENCE: Uh.

00:37:13.565 --> 00:37:15.080
GARY CATONA: Here we go.

00:37:15.080 --> 00:37:19.916
[SINGING]

00:37:19.916 --> 00:37:20.900
GARY CATONA: Smile.

00:37:20.900 --> 00:37:23.352
Louder.

00:37:23.352 --> 00:37:23.852
